Few references for changes in main build.gradle

The use of maven plugin somehow also enables the zipDist and hence gradle starts creating and publishing the distribution in zip format also in addition to tar. So to disable that 2 steps are required

```
  //Avoid generating the zip files from maven installations
            distZip {
                enabled false
            }

            configurations.archives.with {
                artifacts.remove artifacts.find { it.archiveTask.is distZip }
            }
```

First part disables distZip but then it cause issue in install. So zip artifact needs to be explicitly removed. See discussion [here][1]

[1]: https://discuss.gradle.org/t/how-to-exclude-zip-only-from-archives-for-maven-repo-upload/13354/2

